6/19 (Sun.) Wheels and wheelchairs team up for high speed fun/VR headsets help stressed NHS staff escape reality(Host:Danny)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:35-9:00 pm Debate<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Wheels and wheelchairs team up for high speed fun<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/av/disability-61812831">https://www.bbc.com/news/av/disability-61812831</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />1.  How do you feel after watching the video?<br />2.  What is good about helping others?<br />3.  Can you tell me last time what you do to help others? Or being helped?<br /><br />VR headsets help stressed NHS staff escape reality<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/av/uk-wales-61806128">https://www.bbc.com/news/av/uk-wales-61806128</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />1.  How do you feel after watching the video? Do you think that a good way to relieve stress?<br />2.  What kinds of thing would make you feel stressful?<br />3.  How do you tackle stress in your life share your own experience?<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Fri Jun 17, 2022 12:59 am</p><hr />
